				<title>咖啡胶囊走到拐点：Lavazza环保包装创新，正在重写4 billion美元单杯咖啡生意</title>
				<link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/ka-pei-xiao-nang-zou-dao-guai-dian-lavazzahuan-bao/</link>
